{"tid":425341,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢中廢老] 淨係識得欺善怕惡","createTime":"2017-10-05T15:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T17:09:10.000Z","uid":49745,"like":67,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7244ae74beec2fdeca0e22ec8931dcdfa7732813","tid":425341,"uid":49745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:48:08.000Z","msg":"今日天氣好熱 連15分鐘路程都唔想行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n決定搭小巴返屋企 排隊嗰時前面有個女中學生<br />\n後面就一個廢中 一個廢老<br />\n<br />\n到有車嗰時個司機無啦啦飛站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個廢中就開始屌鳩前面個中學生同我<br />\n話係咪搭車架 唔係就唔好企係到啦<br />\n個中學生唔敢出聲 我本身都唔諗住理佢<br />\n<br />\n點知佢講講吓<br />\n個廢老又突然之間插把口入黎一齊鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我頂唔順話返佢地<br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我唔係搭車唔通企係到遮太陽<br />\n 呢個小巴站得一架車經佢見到人排隊 都唔停車又關我事既<br />\n你咁叻你唔去截停佢<br />\n<br />\n廢中即刻冇聲中 個廢老見我駁嘴就即刻轉晒<br />\n話係個司機飛站唔啱 都唔係好關我地事<br />\n<br />\n所以站啲廢中廢老真係唔屌唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：樓主屌得好，廢老唔屌唔安樂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：識唔識尊重下啲老人家"},{"pid":"ce2dce2015193a6c1cdc867b07c8f6e2704ab16c","tid":425341,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:04:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea25b78f3595bb09d3066b87869c292a416f7358","tid":425341,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:04:44.000Z","msg":"投乜撚票呀 又洗正評搏存在感?"},{"pid":"994feba7f207ef24b4fdd29166117522816c9ee7","tid":425341,"uid":49745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實上 你就係冇還口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係有開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb